所有软件包的分层结构

软件包分层结构：
eastone.common, eastone.common.adapter, eastone.common.bridge, eastone.common.context, eastone.common.context.provider.spring, eastone.common.context.provider.spring.test, eastone.common.convertor, eastone.common.factory, eastone.common.processor, eastone.common.processor.io, eastone.common.test

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • junit.framework.Assert
      • junit.framework.TestCase (implements junit.framework.Test)
        • eastone.common.test.ObjectTest
        • eastone.common.context.provider.spring.test.SpringBeanContextTest
    • eastone.common.context.BeanContextFactory (implements eastone.common.factory.Factory<T,E>)
    • eastone.common.Object
      • eastone.common.processor.AbstractProcessorWithResult<T,E> (implements eastone.common.processor.ProcessorWithResult<T,E>)
        • eastone.common.processor.io.File2BytesProcessor (implements eastone.common.adapter.Adapter<T>, eastone.common.convertor.Convertor<S,T,E>, eastone.common.processor.Processor<E>)
        • eastone.common.processor.io.InputStream2BytesProcessor (implements eastone.common.convertor.Convertor<S,T,E>)
      • eastone.common.processor.io.Bytes2FileProcessor (implements eastone.common.processor.Processor<E>)
      • eastone.common.processor.io.Bytes2OutputStreamProcessor (implements eastone.common.processor.Processor<E>)
    • eastone.common.context.provider.spring.SpringBeanContextProvider<C> (implements eastone.common.context.BeanContext<C>)

接口分层结构

  • eastone.common.adapter.Adapter<T>
  • eastone.common.bridge.BridgeAbstraction<T>
  • eastone.common.bridge.BridgeImplementor
  • eastone.common.context.Context
    • eastone.common.context.BeanContext<C>
  • eastone.common.convertor.Convertor<S,T,E>
  • eastone.common.factory.Factory<T,E>
  • eastone.common.processor.Processor<E>
    • eastone.common.processor.ProcessorWithResult<T,E> (并 extends eastone.common.processor.ResultContainer<T>)
  • eastone.common.processor.ResultContainer<T>
    • eastone.common.processor.ProcessorWithResult<T,E> (并 extends eastone.common.processor.Processor<E>)
